                    "type": "stat_block_element",
                    "subtype": "interaction_ability",
                    "text": "<img alt=\"Single Action\" class=\"actiondark\" src=\"Images\\Actions\\OneAction.png\" style=\"height:15px; padding:0px 2px 0px 2px\"/><img alt=\"Single Action\" class=\"actionlight\" src=\"Images\\Actions\\OneAction_I.png\" style=\"height:15px; padding:0px 2px 0px 2px\"/> (divine, transmutation) A shield archon\u2019s hands can change into a <i>+1 <a aonid=\"298\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">holy</a> <a aonid=\"279\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">striking</a></i><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Weapons\">spear</a> and a <i><a aonid=\"326\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">lesser sturdy shield</a></i> or back into hands. Transforming does not restore any HP to the items, and if either the weapon or shield is fully destroyed, the archon loses that hand until it receives a <a aonid=\"248\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>regenerate</i></a> spell or similar magic. If a shield archon is slain, its weapon and shield can be taken, but they fade into nothingness after 24 hours."
